{
  "stem": "1530.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 29.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he said we killed our mother by not being religious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very stubborn man, and so were we.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Coming from Auschwitz, you're just not going to do this to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were waiting for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And an-- and an American soldier wrote us a letter that found my brother in Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was shot on the leg, but he's all right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you're going to hear from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we just took that for granted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we felt, all throughout, my brother is going to remain alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because he wants the world to know about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To be a witness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he was-- from the moment he was liberated, he was working on Jewish programs, and organized everything in Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was just-- he's still a very bright fellow and very good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's very much like my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's just giving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His whole life is giving to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, let's see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived in May, until the fall, September.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's my--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was unbelievably hard, because we just fought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, 50 years later, now, I can say to myself, I don't blame my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He couldn't do anything than what he did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to let us go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to leave him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because Auschwitz made these kind of non-believe-- non-believing people out of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father couldn't accept that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this wasn't in 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was already years later, that I came to this conclusion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't think I could--",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
